**Functional Requirements:**

RF01 — Select products from stock
RF02 — Allow input of quantity received and date of entry
RF03 — Remove products from stock
RF04 — Validate merchandise availability
RF05 — Automatically update stock
RF06 — Record movements

**Non-functional Requirements:**

RNF01 — Simple interface
RNF02 — Respond in a few seconds
RNF03 — Maintain accurate records
RNF04 — Maintain data consistency
RNF05 — Ensure data integrity when entering products
RNF06 — Ensure data integrity when removing products
